        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-10 mx-auto">
            <h4>This tutorial is useful for</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Those who haven’t used  version control before</li>
              <li>Those who have used git GUI but not command line</li>
            </ul>

            <p>Git is a type of <a href="">version control system</a> called Distributed version control system
            </p>
<!-- 
